data.description: THIS PROPERTY IS LOCATED IN THE HIGHLY DESIRED FOOTHILLS OF THE HUALAPIA MOUNTAINS. THE HOME HAS IT'S OWN PRIVATE WELL AND SITS ON JUST UNDER 2 ACRES WITH 360 VIEWS OF THE MOUNTAINS AND THE CITY LIGHTS IN THE EVENING. VA BUYERS CAN ASSUME THE LOAN 4.5% INTEREST. THIS CUSTOM HOME IS JUST OVER 2,700 SQ FT OF LIVING SPACE, 4 SPACIOUS BEDROOMS, 3 BATHROOMS AND 4 CAR GARAGE. THE GARAGE IS BOAT DEEP AND HAS CEILING RACKS FOR EXTRA STORAGE. THERE IS RV PARKING WITH 50 AMPS HOOKUPS, TANKLESS WATER HEATER. THE FRONT AND BACK ARE LANDSCAPED WITH MATURE TREES, SHRUBS AND A FEW NEW TREES THAT WERE JUST RECENTLY PLANTED. THERE IS AN ENORMOUS ENCLOSED COVERED BACK PATIO TO ENTERTAIN & WATCH THE AZ SUNSET! ANOTHER WONDERFUL FEATURE OF THIS HOME IS THE IMPRESSIVE KITCHEN; ALTER WOOD KITCHEN CABINETS, CUTLERY DRAW AND SLIDE CUTTING BOARD,LIGHT UNDERNEATH CABINETS, GRANITE COUNTERTOPS, BUILT IN WINE RACK, BREAKFAST BAR, DUAL OVENS AND STAINLESS STEEL APPLAINCES ALONG WITH A NICE SIZED KITCHEN ISLAND. THERE IS VAULTED CEILINGS, POT SHELVES, FULL ALARM WITH MOTION DETECTORS AND WINDOW CRASH SENSORS, WINDOWS, STEREO WIRED WITH CEILING SPEAKERS, AND ON BACK PATIO RECESSED LIGHTING, CROWN MOLDING, BUILT IN ENTERTAINMENT CENTER, CEILING FANS THROUGHOUT, WINDOW TREATMENTS THROUGHOUT, & THE PICTURE WINDOW IS AN AUTO BLIND. THERE IS A FORMAL AND CAUSAL DINING AREA. INDOOR LAUNDRY ROOM WITH BUILT IN CABINETS. THE PRIMARY SUITE HAS DUAL WALK-IN CLOSETS, FRENCH DOORS LEADING OUT TO THE ENCLOSED BACK PATIO, SEE THROUGH GAS FIREPLACE, DUAL SINKS, JETTED TUB WITH A SEPERATE WALK-IN TILED SHOWER-2 SHOWER HEADS. VA BUYERS CAN ASSUME LOAN AT 4.5% INTEREST
